    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Bratislava Town Council (Augsburg, 3 April
                    1548)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">As requested, Oláh has intervened with the King with the
                            articuli that were sent the other day, and he has managed to secure a
                            good offer. They should know that Oláh always represents their interests
                            with benevolence, and he is attaching the King’s response to Gáspár
                            Serédy in the matter they share with him. Mihály Mérey will tell them
                            about the rest of the matters pertaining to them, as well as the King’s
                            response.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Prudentes et Circumspecti Domini, Amici nobis Honorandi, salutem et
                    obsequiorum nostrorum commendationem!</p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Miseratis nuper cum litteris vestris ad nos articulos quosdam
                    certorum negotiorum vestrorum, rogaveratisque nos per easdem litteras vestras,
                    ut in eisdem articulis apud <persName>regiam maiestatem</persName>, dominum
                    nostrum clementissimum intercederemus, relationemque vobis bonam
                        impetraremus.<note xml:id="note.1">See Ep.
                            682.<ref>olahus.tei.15480225_2</ref></note> Sciatis nos pro nostra in
                    vos benevolentia et studio in eisdem negotiis vestris apud suam maiestatem
                    intercessisse et litteras suae maiestatis ratione<note xml:id="note.2">Uncertain
                        reading.</note> negotii, quod cum domino <persName>Gaspare Seredy</persName>
                    commune habetis, ad eundem dominum Seredy datas praesentibus annexas ad vos
                    misisse. De reliquis autem rebus et negotiis vestris, quid sua maiestas
                    responderit, Dominationibus Vestris per egregium dominum <persName>Michaelem
                        Merey</persName><note xml:id="note.3">Mihály Mérey.</note> brevi
                    significabimus. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Dominationes Vestras feliciter valere optamus.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">Datum <placeName>Augustae Vindelicorum</placeName> tertia Aprilis
                    1548.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Nicolaus Olahus episcopus Zagrabiensis
                            cancellarius regiae maiestatis etc. manu propria</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.6">Prudentibus et circumspectis dominis iudici et iuratis ceterisque
                    civibus civitatis Posoniensis etc. dominis et amicis nobis honorandis.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
